    </p>

    <h2>Note on Audio</h2>
    <p>Audio recording and playback are currently unavailable until community funding is secured to ensure proper hosting and permissions. Thank you for your understanding.</p>

    <p style="margin-top:30px;font-size:13px;color:#7a6a5f;">Developed with respect and care for Indigenous knowledge systems. This project honours the communities who share their languages and stories.</p>
